cubator.com/2538/',18,'nav_menu_item','',0),(2542,1,'2017-10-24 02:55:05','2017-10-24 02:55:05','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 class=\"page-title\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Curriculum</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_id=\"train-1\"][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #035b87;\">Level 1 – Foundation Level of Test Automation</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><strong><span class=\"s1\">(If Evening Course – 4 weeks, 2 times a week, 2 hr classes + lab, homework, exams )</span></strong></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color=\"custom\" accent_color=\"#4dc1ee\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Introduction  </b></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"s1\">Welcome and introduction to what will be covered in course</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"s1\">Software application development process</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"s1\">Example of web application and test automation</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"s1\">Setting up Selenium IDE and using it for test automation</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Selenium Overview, Introduction and setting up project</b></span></h4>\r\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">What is Selenium WebDriver and what was the need for it?</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Introduction as tool for web application test automation</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">The needs for test automation and how it fulfills them</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Cross browser testing</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Building custom test automation frameworks, full programming support needed</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Introducing WebDriver History</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Setting up Eclipse, Java, JUnit and WebDriver libraries</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Creating and running tests on the setup</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Introduction to HTML, CSS, Javascript and support tools</b></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Introduction to HTML, CSS, Javascript and multiple support tools</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b> Introduction to Java</b></span></h4>\r\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Overview</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li5\"><span class=\"s4\">JVM</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">OOP, classes and objects</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Basic data types</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Variable types</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Loops</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Decision making</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">String</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li4\"><span class=\"s1\">Array</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Commonly Used Selenium methods/Apis using WebDriver</b></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"p6\"><span class=\"s1\">Understanding and creating basic test templates</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Basic Selenium constructs interfaces and documentation</b></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"s1\">Basic Constructs of WebDriver</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"s1\">WebDriver Interface</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"s1\">WebElement Interface</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"s1\">By Class</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"s1\">Introduction to WebDriver documentation</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>End to End testing and summing up</b></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"p6\"><span class=\"s1\">Exam, Grading, Certification</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_id=\"train-2\"][vc_column_inner][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #035b87;\">Level 2 – Intermediate Level of Test Automation</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><strong><span class=\"s1\">( If Evening Course – 6.5 weeks, 2 times a week, 2 hr classes + lab, homework, exams )</span></strong></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color=\"custom\" accent_color=\"#4dc1ee\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Introduction &amp; WebDriver Interfaces</b></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"p6\"><span class=\"s1\">Introduction to various WebDriver Interfaces and methods</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">UI/WebElement Locating Strategies using WebDriver (Coverage of By Class)</span><span class=\"s1\"><b>                        </b></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Introduction to Github  What is SCM</b></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">What is Github</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">What is Git</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">UI interface and command line interface</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Installation</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">What is repository?</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Creating a repository</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Master vs Branch</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Cloning a repository</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">How to make and commit code</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Synchronising</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Comparing differences</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Conflict resolution</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>WebDriver Interfaces – Part2<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></b></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"p6\"><span class=\"s1\">Handling_Typical_TestScenarios_Using_WebDriver</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Covering lleftover methods from the list below</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"p6\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Webdriver      </b></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">findElement(By by)</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">findElements(By by)</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">get(java.lang.String url)</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">getCurrentUrl()</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">getPageSource()</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">getTitle()</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">getWindowHandle()</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">getWindowHandles()</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">manage()</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">navigate()</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">switchTo()</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>                           </b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>WebElement<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></b></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">clear()</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">click()</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">findElement(By by)</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">findElements(By by)</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">getAttribute(java.lang.String name)</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">getCssValue(java.lang.String propertyName)</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">getLocation()</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"s1\">getSize()</span></li>\r\n