t size</h3>\r\nNo matter how large or small of a project. We will tackle your project with the same straightforward business approach. No sales negotiation, just expert developers and testers who are the best at what they do. If your project is something more than bug hunting and test automation, then send us an email and we will sort it out right there.\r\n<h3>A complete QA team in a few hours</h3>\r\nIsn’t that the point of “On Demand”? Maybe you only need a few hours of unit testing. Maybe you need more. With our model, you will have a skilled QA crew of expert testers available whenever needed to make bug hunting and automated testing a breeze.\r\n<h3>Transparent Bug Reporting</h3>\r\nYou don\'t need special skills to read our bug reports. When we find a bug you’ll get a ticket that shows you how to reproduce it, what login we used, what we were running and as many screenshots as you need to find the bug and remove it. All bugs will be added in real time into a mutually accessible bug tracking data base. A daily summary report will be submitted at the end of each test-day, summarizing any high priority issues.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Some of our Clients</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\"][vc_column][vc_images_carousel images=\"2658,2659,2660,2661,2662,2663,2664,2665,2666,2667,2668,2669,2670,2671,2672,2673,2674,2675\" img_size=\"\" onclick=\"link_no\" speed=\"2000\" slides_per_view=\"6\" autoplay=\"yes\" hide_pagination_control=\"yes\" wrap=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1>Our Services</h1>\r\nCONTACT QAUBER today, and you could have new test results by tomorrow!\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"no-margin-padding\" width=\"7/12\"][vc_column_text]Quality Assurance On-Demand\r\n\r\nDo you have necessary QA resources availabl