rs that will justify why there’s a need to give attention to your business/company’s quality assurance.\r\n\r\n<strong>Formula #1 – What is the role of QA?\r\n</strong>It is a critical point that takes up a role in the development. We do have software build up specifically for a certain project of our business or company. How ever we have envision it to be perfect, things can go awry and we do know that glitches happening is quite possible. So with quality assurance for software development can turn the tables around if we can run them in certain tests that will guarantee its completeness and usability.  By giving attention to this can help you secure the efficiency of your software hence a bigger possibility of meeting the desired result for your business/company.\r\n\r\n<strong>Formula #2 – Benefits in one whole package</strong>\r\nSoftware quality assurance process isn’t just a “1-2-3 method”. Testing software is something to be taken care of expert hands. Being skilled on this kind of process is important so you can be assured that you’ll get the best result in one whole package. Through QA process, you get to build your software strong making it less chances of making your customers unhappy. You get to test first the efficiency of everything before launching or presenting them to the market. If you get to know beforehand what might be the problem or which part can be improved or in need of change, you can then tweak it in a way it should be – a sure way to be armed and ready for anything that might befall you in your journey to success.\r\n\r\n<strong>Formula #3 – “QA = Wider Reach = Business Success”</strong>\r\nWith quality assurance you get to equate it with opening the door of opportunity, a way to reach more of your possible clients and customers hence making you even nearer to your business/company’s success.\r\n\r\nSo are you looking for the one who understand the importance and true meaning of quality? Are you wondering where can you find the one who ca