t in a way it should be – a sure way to be armed and ready for anything that might befall you in your journey to success.\r\n\r\n<strong>Formula #3 – “QA = Wider Reach = Business Success”</strong>\r\nWith quality assurance you get to equate it with opening the door of opportunity, a way to reach more of your possible clients and customers hence making you even nearer to your business/company’s success.\r\n\r\nSo are you looking for the one who understand the importance and true meaning of quality? Are you wondering where can you find the one who can help you throughout the software quality assurance process? The answer is QAUBER – where quality assurance is ultimately prioritized; hence denoting the meaning of the word “Uber”.\r\n\r\n<em>Here’s a fun fact: Uber is a word meaning extreme, ultimate, best and originally a German language which pertains to above, over or across.</em>\r\n\r\nWant to know more? Simply go to our website : <a href=\"http://qauber.com/\">http://qauber.com</a> to see more of how we can help you with quality assurance!','QUALITY ASSURANCE – THE MISSING LINK IN THE FORMULA OF YOUR BUSINESS’ SUCCESS!','','inherit','closed','closed','','3127-revision-v1','','','2017-11-08 12:57:15','2017-11-08 12:57:15','',3127,'http://www.talcubator.com/3127-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3129,4,'2017-11-08 13:05:22','2017-11-08 13:05:22','With the ever-growing technological world, various software companies have been rising and dominating majority of the business industries. Development and creation of programs and platforms to make the work easier and more accurate are becoming common. However, in order to make sure that the software applications will run systematically and function the way they are envisioned to be, software quality assurance testing must be performed.\r\n\r\nMost software development companies consider quality testing as a centralized function that support and complete software creation. The processes involve a team of engineers and testers who perform detailed step-by-step directions. Each stage must be executed properly in order to achieve the most adequate results. This allows the testers to learn, react and change their approach if needed. Unexpected change in the program or product is always possible along the process.\r\n\r\n<strong>The Ever Changing Processes of Software Development</strong>\r\n\r\nAs years go by, traditional quality testing is losing its ground as competitive companies are sprouting everywhere. More than a decade ago, it has been outsourced extensively due to increase in the cost of significant infrastructure, resource wages and currency fluctuations. It has forced the quality assurance team to increase their mindset and processes to achieve successful automation.\r\n\r\nSo in order to catch up with the rapid change on development, a good QA testing team must constantly try and change their test approaches. To shift from traditional testing methods to agile testing, engineers and testers must be highly knowledgeable, skilled and visionaries to run and discover relevant software testing methodologies. The new shift must enable them to support continuous delivery and integration. It must also allow enabling and disabling of features in the configuration settings.\r\n\r\nIn B2B marketplaces and industries where software applications play a major role, it is more crucial to perform quality assurance testing. From cloud-based testing to agile testing in large scale communications systems, there is an impressive growth in automated testing. Thus, software engineers and testers are becoming in demand and of high importance.\r\n\r\n<strong>Effective Software Quality Assurance Team</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be considered and trusted as efficient quality assurance testers, the team must have a sound and solid understanding of the agile methods, from the testing principles, techniques and practices. These are the foundations to make important decisions on what, how and when to automate. They 